sp_scores.title: Exploit Scarmiglione's weakness to holy attacks.
Defeat Scarmiglione without using fire attacks.

tip_battle.message: Hit Scarmiglione with fire and he'll retaliate with Gas, hitting the whole party with debuffs! Even melee attacks can inspire him to sing a Cursed Elegy and slow your whole party, so watch out, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Scarmiglione

sp_scores.title: Exploit Rubicante's weakness to ice attacks.
Exploit Rubicante's weakness to water attacks.

tip_battle.message: Rubicante is usually vulnerable to ice and water, but when he raises his cape to defend, those elements actually heal him, kupo! Time your attacks just right or things will not go well for you!
tip_battle.title: Rubicante

sp_scores.title: Exploit Cagnazzo's weakness to ice attacks.
Disrupt Cagnazzo's Tsunami with lightning attacks.

tip_battle.message: Cagnazzo's powerful Tsunami ability can be stopped by hitting him with a lightning attack while he's gathering water, kupo! If you're looking for lightning, Thunder is always a good place to start.
tip_battle.title: Cagnazzo

sp_scores.title: Disrupt Barbariccia's tornado form with Jump.

tip_battle.message: If you use physical attacks on Barbariccia while she's in tornado form, she'll hit back with a powerful counterattack, kupo! But not to worry! Using Jump will knock her right out of her tornado form! Make sure to bring someone who can Jump, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Barbariccia

dungeons.epilogue: Cecil's party advanced through the Giant of Babil toward the CPU in order to destroy it, fighting the four Archfiends once more on their way.
dungeons.name: Giant of Babil, Part 1
dungeons.prologue: On the Red Moon, Fusoya tells Cecil of the Lunarian Zemus's maniacal plans to activate the Giant of Babil and use it to destroy the Earth. The party returns to Earth and enters the giant...

sp_scores.title: Defeat Demon Wall without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Demon Wall moves steadily toward the party, kupo! If it gets too close, it will use Crush to instantly KO everyone! Use Slow to buy some time, then beat it down with physical attacks. Attacking with magic will trigger its Stone Gaze counterattack, so watch out!
tip_battle.title: Demon Wall

dungeons.epilogue: Inside the Sealed Cave, the party had defeated Demon Wall and claimed the final crystal when they heard Golbez's voice, and Kain was once again possessed. Under Golbez's influence, Kain wrested the crystal from Cecil and took it away to his master.
dungeons.name: Sealed Cave
dungeons.prologue: Cecil and his allies board Cid's newly repaired airship, the Falcon, to enter the Sealed Cave and claim the final crystal.

sp_scores.title: Exploit the Antlion's weakness to ice attacks.

tip_battle.message: Take care when using physical attacks on the Antlion; it will counter with its deadly Pincer attack, kupo! Bombard it with magic to defeat it!
tip_battle.title: Antlion

dungeons.epilogue: Fending off the attack of a normally docile antlion, Cecil and his allies obtain the Sand Pearl which they use to cure Rosa of Desert Fever. Once she has recovered, she tells them of the Red Wings commander Golbez who was responsible for the attack on Damcyan. She reveals that he now manipulates the king of Baron in a plan to seize the crystals.
dungeons.name: Antlion's Den
dungeons.prologue: Edward lends the party his hovercraft so that they may cross the desert and enter the Antlion's Den in search of the Sand Pearl in hopes it will be the cure they seek.

sp_scores.title: Afflict Sandy with Silence.
Afflict Cindy with Silence.
Afflict Mindy with Silence.

tip_battle.message: The Magus Sisters' Delta Attack is very deadly, kupo! What's worse, Cindy will revive her sisters if they get KO'd, so take Cindy out first!
tip_battle.title: Magus Sisters

dungeons.epilogue: The Magus Sisters in the Tower of Zot unleashed their Delta Attack on the party, but Cecil and his allies emerged victorious. Encountering Golbez, Cecil relinquished the Earth Crystal, yet Golbez refused to release Rosa. Tellah forfeited his own life to cast Meteor in vengeance for the death of his daughter, wounding but not destroying Golbez. Golbez fled, his power over Kain broken.
dungeons.name: Tower of Zot
dungeons.prologue: The Earth Crystal now in Cecil's possession, Kain guides the party to the Tower of Zot where Golbez holds Rosa prisoner. They climb the tower, making for the top.

sp_scores.title: Exploit the Dark Elf's weakness to fire attacks.

tip_battle.message: The Dark Elf is vulnerable to fire, so bring out the fire magic, kupo! Just remember to watch out for his Dark Breath attack when he changes into the Dark Dragon. It can take out your whole party at once, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Dark Elf

dungeons.epilogue: Reunited with Edward in Troia after the shipwreck, the party received the Whisperweed while the bard stayed behind to recuperate. Cecil and his allies then ventured to the Lodestone Cavern in search of the Dark Elf who stole the Earth Crystal. Within the cavern, a powerful magnetic field rendered all metallic armor and weapons useless, and the heroes were hard-pressed to withstand the Dark Elf's attack until the melody of Edward's harp reverberated from the Whisperweed, weakening their foe. Prevailing, the party secured the Earth Crystal.
dungeons.name: Lodestone Cavern
dungeons.prologue: Golbez has demanded the Earth Crystal in exchange for Rosa's safe return, so now Cecil and his allies must pursue the Dark Elf who stole the Crystal from Troia.

sp_scores.title: Defeat Calca and Brina before they combine.

tip_battle.message: Once you take out all of the Calcas or the Brinas, whoever's left will fuse into Calcabrina! Use multi-target attacks to take them all out at once and keep them from fusing, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Calcabrina

sp_scores.title: Exploit Golbez's window of weakness to fire attacks.
Exploit Golbez's window of weakness to ice attacks.
Exploit Golbez's window of weakness to lightning attacks.

tip_battle.message: When you fight Golbez, be sure to take down the Shadow Dragon first, kupo! If you don't, its Shadow Fang attack will knock you out fast! Bring along someone who can cast Raise or Revive just to be on the safe side!
tip_battle.title: Golbez

dungeons.epilogue: Cecil's party visited the Dwarven Castle in the Underworld, where they explained their circumstances to King Giott. Once in the Crystal Chamber, the party fought Golbez and his minions, prevailing against Golbez's magic thanks to the arrival of Rydia and her summoned dragon. Still, Golbez survived and managed to steal away with the Crystal.
dungeons.name: Dwarven Castle
dungeons.prologue: Though Golbez has stolen all four Crystals, the party learns that four more Dark Crystals exist in the Underworld. Now they make for the Dwarven Castle to defend its Crystal from Golbez.

sp_scores.title: Exploit the Mist Dragon's weakness to dark attacks.
Defeat the Mist Dragon without having any attacks countered.

tip_battle.message: The Mist Dragon turns into its mist form every few turns. If you hit it while it's in mist form, it will strike back with a powerful counterattack, kupo! So wait till it changes back before attacking!
tip_battle.title: Mist Dragon

dungeons.epilogue: Cecil and Kain arrive in Mist after slaying the Mist Dragon, only to face a throng of bombs that springs from the Carnelian Signet and engulfs the village in flames. Though furious at being used by the king to destroy the village, there is little they can do, and the two are separated in the chaos. Cecil escapes with a young girl who survived the violence and the two wander the desert before eventually arriving at the oasis of Kaipo.
dungeons.name: Mist Cave
dungeons.prologue: The King of Baron has ordered Cecil of the Red Wings to deliver the Carnelian Signet to the village of Mist.

sp_scores.title: Exploit the CPU's weakness to lightning attacks.
Defeat the CPU without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: If you defeat the Attack Node and the Defense Node before the CPU, the CPU will unleash its deadly Globe 199 attack, dealing enough damage to instantly KO just about anybody, kupo! So take these enemies down in the right order, starting with the Attack Node!
tip_battle.title: CPU, Attack Node, & Defense Node

dungeons.epilogue: Cecil's party reached the heart of the Giant of Babil and succeeded in destroying its CPU. Golbez is furious, until Fusoya breaks Zemus's control over him, and Golbez remembers that he is Cecil's brother, and son to the Lunarian Kluya.
dungeons.name: Giant of Babil, Part 2
dungeons.prologue: As the Giant of Babil wreaks destruction around it, Cecil's party makes their way toward the heart of the giant and the CPU.

sp_scores.title: Defeat Demon Wall without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Demon Wall moves steadily toward the party, kupo! If it gets too close, it will use Crush to instantly KO everyone! Use Slow to buy some time, then beat it down with physical attacks. Attacking with magic will trigger its Stone Gaze counterattack, so watch out!
tip_battle.title: Demon Wall

dungeons.epilogue: Inside the Sealed Cave, the party had defeated Demon Wall and claimed the final crystal when they heard Golbez's voice, and Kain was once again possessed. Under Golbez's influence, Kain wrested the crystal from Cecil and took it away to his master.
dungeons.name: Sealed Cave
dungeons.prologue: Cecil and his allies board Cid's newly repaired airship, the Falcon, to enter the Sealed Cave and claim the final crystal.

Defeat the Mist Dragon without having any attacks countered.

tip_battle.message: The Mist Dragon turns into its mist form every few turns. If you hit it while it's in mist form, it will strike back with a powerful counterattack, kupo! So wait till it changes back before attacking!
tip_battle.title: Mist Dragon

dungeons.prologue: The King of Baron has ordered Cecil of the Red Wings to deliver the Carnelian Signet to the village of Mist.

sp_scores.title: Exploit the Octomammoth's weakness to dark attacks.
Exploit the Octomammoth's weakness to lightning attacks.
Defeat the Octomammoth without having any water attacks absorbed.

tip_battle.message: The Octomammoth is vulnerable to lightning and darkness. Try using the black mage's Lightning and Darkbolt abilities on it, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Octomammoth

dungeons.epilogue: The party assists Tellah the sage in ridding the Underground Waterway of the ferocious Octomammoth, then make their way to Damcyan Castle, only to find it has been sacked by the Red Wings. Amidst the rubble, they find Prince Edward who is lost in grief for his beloved. Though Rydia, who herself lost family, is unimpressed with the prince's behavior, Cecil extends a hand and invites him to join them.
dungeons.name: Underground Waterway
dungeons.prologue: Cecil finds his beloved Rosa in Kaipo, only to learn she languishes with the deadly Desert Fever. He sets out for Damcyan to find a cure.

sp_scores.title: Defeat the King of Eblan without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: The King and Queen of Eblan use fire attacks, so outfit your party with equipment that gives fire resistance to turn down the heat, kupo!
tip_battle.title: King and Queen of Eblan

sp_scores.title: Exploit Rubicante's weakness to ice attacks.
Exploit Rubicante's weakness to water attacks.

tip_battle.message: Rubicante is usually vulnerable to ice and water, but when he raises his cape to defend, those elements actually heal him, kupo! Time your attacks just right or things will not go well for you!
tip_battle.title: Rubicante

dungeons.epilogue: Edge was reunited with his parents, the King and Queen of Eblan, only to see them transform into monsters and attack. Just before their death, Edge's parents regained their senses and bid their son farewell. Edge's rage awakened his latent power, giving him the strength to defeat Rubicante. Though the party succeeded in entering the Crystal Chamber, the heroes fell through a trapdoor to the Underworld before they were able to retrieve the Crystals.
dungeons.name: Tower of Babil - Heights
dungeons.prologue: In order to retrieve the Crystal, Edge joins Cecil's party as they make their way into the Overworld half of the Tower of Babil.

sp_scores.title: Exploit the Mom Bomb's weakness to ice attacks.
Exploit the Mom Bomb's weakness to dark attacks.
Defeat the Mom Bomb without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: When Mom Bomb's HP gets too low, she explodes big time, kupo! Bring along someone with healing magic to keep your party's HP topped off so they can take the hit!
tip_battle.title: Mom Bomb

dungeons.epilogue: Cecil and his allies rescue the Fabul monk Yang from the rampaging Mom Bomb on the peak of Mount Hobs. Rosa suspects the attack is part of Golbez's plan to lure guards away from Fabul, and Cecil's party joins Yang as they hurry to the city's defense.
dungeons.name: Mount Hobs
dungeons.prologue: Cecil and his party make for Fabul, where lies the Wind Crystal they need to thwart Golbez. But first they must navigate the treacherous, icebound slopes of Mount Hobs.

sp_scores.title: Defeat Bahamut without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Bahamut takes reduced damage from all elemental damage except poison, and if you use magic on him, he casts Reflect! When the countdown ends, he uses Megaflare, so use abilities like Magic Break and Shell first to reduce the damage, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Bahamut

dungeons.epilogue: The party found Bahamut within the Lair of the Father on the Red Moon. Having proved their worth by defeating Leviathan, the party challenged Bahamut and prevailed, and Bahamut lent his strength to Cecil's party.
dungeons.name: Lair of the Father
dungeons.prologue: The mages of Mysidia have raised the Lunar Whale. Now it carries Cecil's party to the Red Moon, where they will face Bahamut.

sp_scores.title: Disrupt Barbariccia's tornado form with Jump.

tip_battle.message: If you use physical attacks on Barbariccia while she's in tornado form, she'll hit back with a powerful counterattack, kupo! But not to worry! Using Jump will knock her right out of her tornado form! Make sure to bring someone who can Jump, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Barbariccia

dungeons.epilogue: Cecil rescued Rosa by a hair's breadth, and the couple was reunited at last. Kain confessed he only wanted to keep Rosa safe, and begged their forgiveness. Together, they vowed to bring an end to Golbez's reign, but their escape route was blocked by Barbariccia. Kain joined the party in defeating Barbariccia, and thanks to Rosa's Teleport spell, they escaped the collapsing Tower of Zot.
dungeons.name: Tower of Zot - Spire
dungeons.prologue: Tellah's Meteor has freed Kain from Golbez's control. But there is little time to rest as the party continues toward the top of the tower and Rosa.

sp_scores.title: Afflict Asura with Reflect.

tip_battle.message: Asura absorbs just about every kind of elemental attack, kupo! It's time to get physical on this boss!
tip_battle.title: Asura

sp_scores.title: Exploit Leviathan's weakness to lightning attacks.

tip_battle.message: Leviathan has lots of attacks that hit the whole party. Having a character with a Soul Break that can heal everyone at once will make this fight much easier, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Leviathan

dungeons.epilogue: Rydia led the way through the Passage of the Eidolons to the Feymarch, where they requested the assistance of the Eidolon King and Queen, Leviathan and Asura. After proving themselves in battle, they secured the Eidolons' help and made for the Sealed Cave where the final Crystal awaited.
dungeons.name: The Feymarch
dungeons.prologue: The last Crystal lies within the Sealed Cave. Before the party attempts to claim the Crystal, they follow Rydia's advice and go to the Passage of the Eidolons in hopes of securing the Eidolons' help.

dungeons.prologue: On the Red Moon, Fusoya tells Cecil of the Lunarian Zemus's maniacal plans to activate the Giant of Babil and use it to destroy the Earth. The party returns to Earth and enters the giant...

sp_scores.title: Defeat the Dragoon without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Kain's Jump ability hits hard, kupo. After it lands, be ready to heal up right away, or it won't be pretty. Oh my, no...
tip_battle.title: Kain

dungeons.epilogue: Together with Yang, Cecil and the party defend Fabul Castle from the forces of Baron. Yet the monsters that Golbez employs prove too much for the heroes to handle, and they are pushed back to the Crystal Chamber. There, the commander of the assault reveals himself to be Cecil's friend Kain. The bewildered Cecil is powerless to resist as Kain and Golbez walk off with Rosa and the crystal.
dungeons.name: Fabul Castle
dungeons.prologue: Its monk warriors decimated, Fabul is in dire straits. Cecil and Edward come to stand with Yang against the forces of Baron.

dungeons.epilogue: The Geraldine monarchy's ninjutsu did little to fend off Rubicante's assault, forcing the survivors from Eblan Castle to make their new home in the Caves of Eblan. Cecil's party watched as Rubicante and the prince of Eblan, Edge, fought near the Tower of Babil, but Edge was no match for the Archfiend. Cecil and the others convinced Edge to join them and pursue Rubicante into the tower.
dungeons.name: Cave of Eblan
dungeons.prologue: The party escapes the Tower and makes for the Overworld. Cid risks his life to stop their pursuers, allowing the party to go through the Cave of Eblan to reach the Overworld levels of the Tower.

dungeons.name: Giant of Babil, Part 2
dungeons.prologue: As the Giant of Babil wreaks destruction around it, Cecil's party makes their way toward the heart of the giant and the CPU.

sp_scores.title: Exploit Barnabas's weakness to lightning attacks.
Defeat Barnabas before he self-destructs.

tip_battle.message: Lugae and Barnabas don't have any special attacks to speak of, kupo. Lugae will heal Barnabas, so take out Lugae first to keep the battle from dragging on!
tip_battle.title: Lugae

sp_scores.title: Exploit Lugaeborg's weakness to lightning attacks.

tip_battle.message: Lugaeborg has powerful group and single target attacks, kupo! But like all machines, it's vulnerable to lightning! Focused lightning attacks should zap it down fast!
tip_battle.title: Lugaeborg

dungeons.epilogue: The party's plan to retrieve the seven Crystals from the Tower of Babil was foiled by Rubicante. Meanwhile, the tower's cannons turned on the dwarven tanks outside, and although the party was able to defeat Dr. Lugae, Golbez's soldiers continued the barrage. It was Yang who managed to disable the cannons, though it nearly cost him his life.
dungeons.name: Tower of Babil - Depths
dungeons.prologue: With three Dark Crystals already in his possession, Golbez now aims to take the fourth and final Crystal. The party seizes this opportunity to make an assault on the Tower of Babil and retrieve the stolen Crystals.

tip_battle.message: If Baigan loses both of his arms, he'll regenerate them, kupo! What's worse, his arms explode if they're still alive when you take down his body! The more HP the arms have when they explode, the more damage they do, so get the arms as low as possible before finishing off Baigan's body!
tip_battle.title: Baigan

dungeons.epilogue: The party has infiltrated Baron Castle via the Ancient Waterway, defeating Cecil's former comrade Baigan and the Archfiend Cagnazzo along the way. Though they are reunited with Cid, Palom and Porom must sacrifice themselves to free the party from Cagnazzo's trap. With hearts heavy over the loss of their companions, the party boards Cid's airship, the Enterprise.
dungeons.name: Baron Castle
dungeons.prologue: Cecil and his allies make their way from Mysidia to Baron along Devil's Road. Rescuing a befuddled Yang from the king's control, they infiltrate Baron Castle.

dungeons.epilogue: Cecil and his allies rescue the Fabul monk Yang from the rampaging Mom Bomb on the peak of Mount Hobs. Rosa suspects the attack is part of Golbez's plan to lure guards away from Fabul proper, and Cecil's party joins Yang as they hurry to the defense of Fabul Castle.
dungeons.name: Mount Hobs
dungeons.prologue: Cecil and his party make for Fabul, where lies the Wind Crystal they need to thwart Golbez. But first they must navigate the treacherous, icebound slopes of Mount Hobs.

sp_scores.title: Exploit Baigan's weakness to ice attacks.
Defeat Baigan before his arms self-destruct.

tip_battle.message: If Baigan loses both of his arms, he'll regenerate them, kupo! What's worse, his arms explode if they're still alive when you take down his body! The more HP the arms have when they explode, the more damage they do, so get the arms as low as possible before finishing off Baigan's body!
tip_battle.title: Baigan

sp_scores.title: Disrupt Cagnazzo's Tsunami with lightning attacks.
Exploit Cagnazzo's weakness to ice attacks.

tip_battle.message: Cagnazzo's powerful Tsunami ability can be stopped by hitting him with a lightning attack while he's gathering water, kupo! If you're looking for lightning, Thunder is always a good place to start.
tip_battle.title: Cagnazzo

dungeons.epilogue: The party has infiltrated Baron Castle via the Ancient Waterway, defeating Cecil's former comrade Baigan and the Archfiend Cagnazzo along the way. Though they are reunited with Cid, Palom and Porom must sacrifice themselves to free the party from Cagnazzo's trap.
dungeons.name: Baron Castle
dungeons.prologue: Cecil and his allies make their way from Mysidia to Baron along Devil's Road. Rescuing a befuddled Yang from the king's control, they infiltrate Baron Castle.

sp_scores.title: Exploit the Octomammoth's weakness to dark attacks.
Exploit the Octomammoth's weakness to lightning attacks.
Defeat the Octomammoth without having any water attacks absorbed.

tip_battle.message: The Octomammoth is vulnerable to lightning and darkness. Try using the black mage's Lightning and Darkbolt abilities on it, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Octomammoth

dungeons.epilogue: The party assist Tellah the sage in ridding the Underground Waterway of the ferocious Octomammoth, then make their way to Damcyan Castle, only to find it has been sacked by the Red Wings. Amidst the rubble, they find Prince Edward who is lost in grief for his beloved. Though Rydia, who herself lost family, is unimpressed with the prince's behavior, Cecil extends a hand and invites him to join them.
dungeons.name: Underground Waterway
dungeons.prologue: Cecil finds his beloved Rosa in Kaipo, only to learn she languishes with the deadly Desert Fever. He sets out for Damcyan to find a cure.

sp_scores.title: Exploit the Antlion's weakness to ice attacks.

tip_battle.message: Take care when using physical attacks on the Antlion; it will counter with its deadly Pincer attack, kupo! Bombard it with magic to defeat it!
tip_battle.title: Antlion

dungeons.epilogue: Fending off the attack of a normally docile antlion, Cecil and his allies obtain the Sand Pearl which they use to cure Rosa's Desert Fever. Once she has recovered, she tells them of the Red Wing commander Golbez who was responsible for the attack on Damcyan. She reveals that he now manipulates the king of Baron in a plan to seize the crystals.
dungeons.name: Antlion's Den
dungeons.prologue: Edward lends the party his hovercraft so that they may cross the desert and enter the Antlion's Den in search of the Sand Pearl in hopes it will be the cure they seek.

sp_scores.title: Defeat Calca and Brina before they combine.

tip_battle.message: Once you take out all of the Calcas or the Brinas, whoever's left will fuse into Calcabrina! Use multi-target attacks to take them all out at once and keep them from fusing, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Calcabrina

sp_scores.title: Exploit Golbez's window of weakness to fire attacks.
Exploit Golbez's window of weakness to ice attacks.
Exploit Golbez's window of weakness to lightning attacks.

tip_battle.message: When you fight Golbez, be sure to take down the Shadow Dragon first, kupo! If you don't, its Shadow Fang attack will knock you out fast! Bring along someone who can cast Raise or Revive just to be on the safe side!
tip_battle.title: Golbez

dungeons.epilogue: Cecil's party visited the Dwarven Castle in the Underworld, where they explained their circumstances to King Giott. Once in the Crystal Chamber, the party fought Golbez and his minions, prevailing against Golbez's magic thanks to the arrival of Rydia and her summoned dragon. Still, Golbez survived and managed to steal away with the Crystal.
dungeons.name: Dwarven Castle
dungeons.prologue: Though Golbez has stolen all four Crystals, the party learns that four more Dark Crystals exist in the Underworld. Now they make for the Dwarven Castle to defend its Crystal from Golbez.

sp_scores.title: Exploit Barnabas's weakness to lightning attacks.
Defeat Barnabas before he self-destructs.

tip_battle.message: Lugae and Barnabas don't have any special attacks to speak of, kupo. Lugae will heal Barnabas, so take out Lugae first to keep the battle from dragging on!
tip_battle.title: Lugae

sp_scores.title: Exploit Lugaeborg's weakness to lightning attacks.

tip_battle.message: Lugaeborg has powerful group and single target attacks, kupo! But like all machines, it's vulnerable to lightning! Focused lightning attacks should zap it down fast!
tip_battle.title: Lugaeborg

dungeons.epilogue: The party's plan to retrieve the seven Crystals from the Tower of Babil was foiled by Rubicante. Meanwhile, the tower's cannons turned on the dwarven tanks outside, and although the party was able to defeat Dr. Lugae, Golbez's soldiers continued the barrage. It was Yang who managed to disable the cannons, though it nearly cost him his life.
dungeons.name: Tower of Babil - Depths
dungeons.prologue: With three Dark Crystals already in his possession, Golbez now aims to take the fourth and final Crystal. The party seizes this opportunity to make an assault on the Tower of Babil and retrieve the stolen Crystals.

sp_scores.title: Afflict Sandy with Silence.
Afflict Cindy with Silence.
Afflict Mindy with Silence.

tip_battle.message: The Magus Sisters' Delta Attack is very deadly, kupo! What's worse, Cindy will revive her sisters if they get KO'd, so take Cindy out first!
tip_battle.title: Magus Sisters

dungeons.epilogue: The Magus Sisters in the Tower of Zot unleashed their Delta Attack on the party, but Cecil and his allies emerged victorious. Encountering Golbez, Cecil relinquished the Earth Crystal, yet Golbez refused to release Rosa. Tellah forfeited his own life to cast Meteor in vengeance for the death of his daughter, wounding but not destroying Golbez. Golbez fled, his power over Kain broken.
dungeons.name: Tower of Zot
dungeons.prologue: The Earth Crystal now in Cecil's possession, Kain guides the party to the Tower of Zot where Golbez holds Rosa prisoner. They climb the tower, making for the top.

sp_scores.title: Disrupt Barbariccia's tornado form with Jump.

tip_battle.message: If you use physical attacks on Barbariccia while she's in tornado form, she'll hit back with a powerful counterattack, kupo! But not to worry! Using Jump will knock her right out of her tornado form! Make sure to bring someone who can Jump, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Barbariccia

dungeons.epilogue: Cecil rescued Rosa by a hair's breadth, and the couple was reunited at last. Kain confessed he only wanted to keep Rosa safe, and begged their forgiveness. Together, they vowed to bring an end to Golbez's reign, but their escape route was blocked by Barbariccia. Kain joined the party in defeating Barbariccia, and thanks to Rosa's Teleport spell, they escaped the collapsing Tower of Zot.
dungeons.name: Tower of Zot - Spire
dungeons.prologue: Tellah's Meteor has freed Kain from Golbez's control. But there is little time to rest as the party continues toward the top of the tower and Rosa.
